Because of the modular and flexible nature of platformOS, you can build your own REST APIs in Liquid markup or build workflows to integrate email, text, or any third-party APIs, and write your own custom integrations. To make building on platformOS easier for you, we provide out of the box integrations with multiple third-party services. Explore a list of integrations we have in this article. 


## Third-party integrations

### Slack

[Slack](https://slack.com/) is a business communication platform developed by [Slack Technologies](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Slack_Technologies), now owned by [Salesforce](https://www.salesforce.com/eu/?ir=1). Slack offers many IRC-style features, including persistent chat rooms (channels) organized by topic, private groups, and direct messaging.

