### Sendgrid

[SendGrid](https://sendgrid.com/) is a customer communication platform for transactional and marketing email. It provides: management of shipping notifications, friend requests, sign-up confirmations, and email newsletters, internet service provider (ISP) monitoring, domain keys, sender policy framework (SPF), and feedback loops, link tracking, open rate reporting, email opened tracking, unsubscribes, bounces, and spam reports. 

