### reCaptcha

​​[reCAPTCHA](https://developers.google.com/recaptcha) is a CAPTCHA system that enables web hosts to distinguish between human and automated access to websites. The original version asked users to decipher hard to read text or match images. Version 2 also asked users to decipher text or match images if the analysis of cookies and canvas rendering suggested the page was being downloaded automatically.<sup> </sup>Since version 3, reCAPTCHA will never interrupt users and is intended to run automatically when users load pages or click buttons. 

