## Modules

platformOS modules allow code reuse and sharing, while protecting the IP of creators. Modules are available on the [pOS Module Marketplace](https://partners.platformos.com/marketplace/pos_modules) after registering and logging in to the [Partner Portal](https://partners.platformos.com/). 


### pOS Sendgrid Email Marketing

The pOS Sendgrid Email Marketing module helps you connect your instance to your Sendgrid Email Marketing account so you can create lists, add users to those lists, and send Sendgrid Campaigns straight from your Instance.

